data.description: WELCOME HOME, to this well-maintained residence, boasting a spacious family room with a fireplace, formal dining room, living area, and a well-appointed eat-in kitchen, ideal for hosting gatherings. The primary bedroom offers a luxurious sitting area, trey ceilings, and an expansive en-suite bathroom.  The property showcases a stunning waterfall staircase with a two-story foyer, complemented by a sizable backyard featuring a patio and shed. This property is located on a corner lot and is conveniently situated near Stonecrest Mall, just 30 minutes from downtown Atlanta, and with easy access to Interstate 285 and Highway 78.  No Homeowners Association which means NO HOA fees apply. Do not miss the opportunity to call this beautiful property, HOME!
